articles.title: Sean 'Diddy' Combs returns lucrative music rights to Bad Boy Records artists - BBC
articles.description: Ma$e, Faith Evans and the estate of the Notorious B.I.G. all regain control of their music.
articles.content:
In a rare move, Sean "Diddy" Combs has returned some music rights to artists and songwriters who were signed to his label, instead of cashing in on them.
